data.eml:eml: A catalogue of the ants of Paraguay (Hymenoptera: Formicidae)

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Wild, Alexander L. (2007): A catalogue of the ants of Paraguay (Hymenoptera: Formicidae). Zootaxa 1622: 1-55, DOI: 10.5281/zenodo.179222
